36:55.109 --> 37:02.109
race for Me, so I'll try to make it short
now - it's the Vishuddhi Chakra as he told

37:02.400 --> 37:09.400
you is very important, this is America. Vishuddhi
Chakra is America in the Universe. America

37:11.470 --> 37:18.470
is the Vishuddhi Chakra and the star is the
