37:29.730 --> 37:36.730
itself. Is a very important thing that this
center is America, so America has the responsibility

37:38.569 --> 37:45.569
of transformation. They have to take up the
responsibility of transforming the whole world.

37:47.829 --> 37:54.829
Instead of that they themselves are getting
ruined, they are killing themselves. There

37:55.140 --> 38:02.140
is no fear from outside I tell you, we are
