38:26.769 --> 38:27.509
responsibility.

38:27.509 --> 38:34.509
This very important center as he must have
told you, by the virtue of this on the gross

38:37.589 --> 38:44.589
we develop a face which is very relaxed and
attractive and good looking. We develop eyes

38:47.309 --> 38:54.309
which are full of compassion; we develop a
face which is innocent, which is very smooth

38:58.440 --> 39:05.440
and which has got a capacity to express its
feeling. The smallest of feelings can be expressed

39:07.369 --> 39:13.859
through this center. It looks after your nose,
yours ears, everything improves with this.

39:13.859 --> 39:20.859
You develop - now I can't hear anything if
a non-Sahaja Yogi speaks to Me. It is a very

39:21.250 --> 39:26.529
funny thing, unless and until that person
