39:26.529 --> 39:32.369
saying, to Me, it is all what you call “blah,
blah, blah.” But a Sahaja Yogi, if he speaks

39:32.369 --> 39:35.019
to Me I can hear very well.

39:35.019 --> 39:42.019
The whole thing changes, the whole sensitivity
changes, you start understanding what music

39:43.960 --> 39:50.960
is good for your Spirit; you start understanding
what is good for your eyes to see, because

39:54.269 --> 39:59.319
you don't want like to see that is something
that is horrid, you just don't enjoy it. You

39:59.319 --> 40:03.000
feel like vomiting - you see something horrid,
you just feel like vomiting. You become so

40:03.000 --> 40:07.950
sensitive you can't imagine, to virtue and
to goodness.

40:07.950 --> 40:14.680
Automatically it happens to you, I don't have
to tell you. I've seen people have changed

40:14.680 --> 40:21.680
overnight. The whole idea is that the light
has to be brought in for you to see for yourself,

40:21.690 --> 40:27.769
and when it happens you'll be amazed, you
become such a different, wonderful person.

40:27.769 --> 40:34.769
There's everyone in America has Abraham Lincoln
within them, which has to be just awakened

40:35.269 --> 40:42.269
and you'll find that that great personality
can be shown in you, when it happens to you.

40:43.430 --> 40:50.430
It has to happen to all of you to feel that
greatness that lies hidden within.

40:50.869 --> 40:56.210
I cannot elaborately tell you about Vishuddhi
Chakra what they call the Krishna consciousness,

40:56.210 --> 41:02.450
but not this Krishna consciousness which has
made people actual beggars, they are begging

41:02.450 --> 41:07.700
on the streets. You go in India in the villages,
about they were going to beat these people.

41:07.700 --> 41:11.749
They thought they are Krishna consciousness,
they wouldn’t get places in the hotels because

41:11.749 --> 41:15.670
they thought they are Krishna consciousness,
because these people were lost, they had no

41:15.670 --> 41:21.269
money left with them. Now they are begging
in India, imagine. How can we afford to have

41:21.269 --> 41:25.279
these beggars there? They have no money with
them, they can not come back, they don't know

41:25.279 --> 41:32.279
what to do with them, so many you will find
in the villages just begging. So this kind

41:32.999 --> 41:39.999
of thing that - imagine a person who is being
blessed by Shri Krishna Who is the Deity on

41:43.369 --> 41:45.829
this center, should beg!

41:45.829 --> 41:52.069
He's the One Who is the giver of complete
wealth, why should we beg? This is the thing

41:52.069 --> 41:58.009
they don't understand, just the opposite of
what they are suppose to be. There are lots

41:58.009 --> 42:04.430
of stories of Krishna how He blessed people
with wealth. It is to be seen sometimes, if

42:04.430 --> 42:09.579
you have time, I may have time then we might
be able to see all those beautiful things

42:09.579 --> 42:12.259
that He did.

