So the other chakra is important, is the Chakra
of Christ. This center is very important because

42:19.990 --> 42:25.680
this is the gate through this you have to
pass to your destination which is the limbic

42:25.680 --> 42:31.240
area. So Christ is the gate, many people are
shouting, “it's only He can save.” Where

42:31.240 --> 42:37.369
is He now? Is He here? When He was living,
they talked of Ibrahim, when He came then

42:37.369 --> 42:42.640
they said, “You are not the One. It was
Moses. You are not the One.”

42:42.640 --> 42:48.150
They denied Him, defied Him. Now when He's
dead, then we think, “It is Christ.” Now

42:48.150 --> 42:54.160
I have come, He's talked about Me, if you
read Bible you'll find He’s talked about

42:54.160 --> 42:59.210
Me very clearly there and I have to do My
job and I have come. You are going to say

42:59.210 --> 43:05.160
that it was Christ Who has to do it. If Christ
could do it, why did He say that “I'm going

43:05.160 --> 43:09.809
to send you a comforter”? He talked of future,
didn’t He? Why did He say such a thing?

43:09.809 --> 43:14.259
We should find out why did He say that “I
will send you the Holy Ghost and the Comforter

43:14.259 --> 43:19.259
and the Redeemer and a Counselor”? Why did
He say that? Why not look forward to that?

43:19.259 --> 43:24.700
Because we are today after Christ. People
don't want to see this point, they want to

43:24.700 --> 43:29.299
depend on Christ because He's in their pocket,
they can use Him the way they like.

43:29.299 --> 43:36.299
When He has talked, He has said, “Why not
see the point?” If this is what Christ is,

43:38.990 --> 43:45.509
then it is such a bad thing because people
say, “Christ was no good.” They say, “What

43:45.509 --> 43:51.470
has Christ given us?” Christians nations,
what have they done, what have they achieved?

43:51.470 --> 43:58.470
It's a bad name to Him if you do not see completion
of His work. I'm here to complete His work

43:59.819 --> 44:05.759
and when you do not complete His work, His
half-work done in a very half-way will bring

44:05.759 --> 44:06.900
bad name to Him.

44:06.900 --> 44:12.130
Why not people who claim about Christ understand
that what others have to say about it? If

44:12.130 --> 44:15.960
you want to know about Christians, go and
ask the Jews; and if you want to know about

44:15.960 --> 44:20.819
the Jews, go and ask the Muslims; and if you
