44:20.819 --> 44:27.819
the Hindus. There are all in a doldrum. Nobody
has any understanding that they are worshiping

44:28.099 --> 44:35.099
or they are admiring or advocating a flower
which belongs to one tree of life. They have

44:35.950 --> 44:42.749
all plucked those flowers, “This is mine,
this is mine, in my pocket,” and fighting.

44:42.749 --> 44:49.749
If religion means fighting and quarreling,
it is not a religion at all. If it is integration,

44:50.569 --> 44:52.869
then it is a religion.

44:52.869 --> 44:59.190
In Sahaja Yoga you'll find that they are all
together. Christ has said, very clearly, “Those

44:59.190 --> 45:06.190
who are not against Me are with Me.” Who
are those people? Try to find out. For that

45:07.069 --> 45:13.130
you have to little bit go out of Bible. In
