45:13.130 --> 45:18.529
for three years? Nobody allowed Him to live
for three years, and if they could, they would

45:18.529 --> 45:20.059
also kill Me.

45:20.059 --> 45:26.170
Not easy, He wanted to play the drama, otherwise
He would have finished all of them, in no

45:26.170 --> 45:33.170
time. So He has said that “You are to be
resurrected first, and then that's how you

45:33.599 --> 45:34.369
will be judged.”

45:34.369 --> 45:40.970
And the Day of Judgment is today, this is
the Day of Judgment, that's why you are confused,

45:40.970 --> 45:44.819
this is the Day of Judgment where you will
be judged and how are you going to be judged?

45:44.819 --> 45:51.730
Through your Kundalini. Your Kundalini is
going to be awakened and you'll be judged

45:51.730 --> 45:55.440
where you are. That's what it is, and those
who will be calling Me, “Christ, Christ”

45:55.440 --> 46:02.380
I will not look at them, that's what it is.
