46:56.059 --> 47:03.059
you rise, thousands and thousands and millions
and millions can be saved. Try to rise, try

47:04.460 --> 47:09.430
to understand your own responsibilities, that
is very important.

47:09.430 --> 47:16.430
Today is the last day and the last center
which is the Sahasrara, is the integration,

47:16.470 --> 47:23.470
integration of your being, of physical, mental,
emotional being, it takes place. Is integration

47:24.809 --> 47:31.009
of all the Deities, of all the Prophets, all
